entry.string: From this screen, you will be adding a documentation for your extension. Please enter all applicable information. Documentation is held for validation. If your extension is certified, your documentation will be syndicated into the help module, as well as notification of the extension status. For more information on the certification of extensions, and their benefits, please read this information (insert link).
entry.translation: Frum thees screee, yuoo veell be-a eddeeng a ducoomenteshun fur yuoor ixtenseeun. Bork bork bork! Pleese-a inter ell eppleeceble-a inffurmeshun. Ducoomenteshun is held fur feleedeshun. Iff yuoor ixtenseeun is certeeffied, yuoor ducoomenteshun veell be-a syndeeceted intu zee help mudoole-a, es vell es nuteefficeshun ooff zee ixtenseeun stetoos. Fur mure-a inffurmeshun oon zee certeefficeshun ooff ixtenseeuns, und zeeur beneffeets, pleese-a reed thees inffurmeshun (insert leenk).
